sentences: Ricky Laureano (born August 3, 1969) is a Puerto Rican musician most known for being the guitarist and one of the main songwriters of the Rock en Espa√±ol band Fiel a la Vega.
In 1990, Laureano and Auger decide to seriously pursue a career in music and they moved to the United States, specifically in New Jersey.

Since 2010, the band has reduced their presentations, which has allowed Laureano to work on his own music.
In 2017, Laureano recorded his first full-length album in which he sang and recorded all the instruments.
Three months later, Auger's father died and he returned to Puerto Rico.
Two years later, upon Auger's return they reunited again.
Since 2010, the band has reduced their presentations, which has allowed Laureano to work on his own music.
